name: The Gambler
description:
Digital Drawing
5511 x 5511 pxl
2021

The visuals insight came from the girl i know. The girl who always do random things for the sake in search of happiness. Main goals of her life, just happy. Not money, fame, power, or another materials things. Just Happy. 

Random things means any activity taht she never plan to do. But at the end, whatever it is, it always lead her to the good way. Even better than any people that plan their lives properly. Better means it always lead her to be happy, so she could be gratefull about her life. 

Seems like a gamble machine, she just pushed the button and then got a Jackpot. Jackpot means the things that searched by other people hardly. But she just get it like easy. The things named, happy.
